descriptionHtml:
NOTE: I\'m very sorry for that \"love letter\" thing you had downloaded before. It was my cousin\'s joke. Hope he won\'t do that again. New version should work like a charm.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
36 to 56 - Safe FPS Booster
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Clever and safe .ini file that stabilises your game\'s performance adding up to 20 FPS plus without losing anything at graphics. Just put into your Skyrim direction folder. Made by me and my cousin who used to work in Novalogic as a Lead Programmer for the game called Delta Force: Xtreme.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
I. INSTALLATION
Just put the SkyrimFPS.ini file into your game\'s direction folder (where the SkyrimLauncher file is).
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
II. COMPATIBILITY
36 to 56 - Safe FPS Booster is possibly (not tested enough to prove it 100%) compatible and safe to run with every modification and other performance boosters for Skyrim. It\'s just a seperate file that doesn\'t invole in anything besides game\'s performance system.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
III. BUGS
Tested on mine\'s Windows 7 computer and on cousin\'s Windows XP laptop. After one day of playing we didn\'t record any bugs at all. But if you notice any during your gameplay - write in comments or PM me.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
IV. CREDITS
Buntownik11cm and NovaLizard81 (but he did most of the job so he deserves more credit than me)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

And remember - if you\'ll encounter any problems during your play with this modification - WRITE ME. We want this booster to be the best as it can get so any help from you is another step to perfection.
author: Buntownik11cm and NovaLizard81
